    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed the required levels for MRL 2. Six factors were appropriately scoped out at MRL 2 for a Class II device with medium model influence. The CFD model demonstrates sufficient credibility to support identification of worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under CPB conditions. The relative hemolysis index predictions are within acceptable agreement with experimental data, and the acceptance criterion of RH < 1.0 is satisfied across all operating points.",
